<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期六，当奥利维亚到的时候，凯蒂正坐在门廊的台阶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在活动她的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在干什么？” 奥利维亚问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看这个，我写的是什么？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚仔细地看着凯蒂的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我写的是字母 ‘A’。” 凯蒂解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是 ‘B’。你好好儿看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她又动了几下腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“医生说我每天都得写几次字母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样的话，我的脚踝就会变得很强壮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，我星期五就能去坐干草车了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你继续写。我去捡核桃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别被蜱虫咬了！” 凯蒂说。奥利维亚笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃完早饭，乔伊就一直在捡核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一看见奥利维亚向山坡上跑来，就马上跑去迎接她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来了！我来帮你了！” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你！” 乔伊把奥利维亚带到手推车附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些树下有非常多的核桃。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看，我已经捡了好多了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸说等装满了这车，我们就能去核桃收购站了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 然后，我们还可以再捡一车！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们来比一比，看谁能先装满自己的桶！” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一次捡起了两个核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟的时间里，只能听见核桃 “咚咚咚” 地被扔进桶里的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“满了！” 乔伊说，“我赢了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们再比一次！” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们把桶里的核桃倒进了手推车，然后继续捡起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 咚！咚！咚！“满了！” 奥利维亚喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们打平了！” 女孩儿们笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然她们是在劳动，但却很有意思。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳越升越高，乔伊沿路捡核桃捡到了树林附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚捡了一桶又一桶，一直捡到了池塘附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那边的草好像又长高了许多。” 乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里是个好地方。” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很多核桃滚到了这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你小心点儿。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心什么？” 奥利维亚问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道的，像毒藤和蜱虫什么的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>总之，一定要小心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚以最快的速度捡起核桃来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很快就捡了满满一桶的核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要创造一个新的世界纪录了！” 她大笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她尖叫了一声。“蛇！” 她喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她试着站起来，可却向后滑倒在草地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她又尖叫了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只是一条黑蛇。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看！它走了。你吓到它了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我吓到蛇了？” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她向乔伊跑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一阵风刮了过来，吹动了树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个核桃掉到了奥利维亚的脚上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 她大叫着，抬头看了一下树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，一个核桃又恰巧掉到了她的鼻子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！好疼！” 她揉着鼻子，又尖叫了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 啊！我的鼻子出血了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，奥利维亚像凯蒂一样，坐在了门廊的台阶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“捏住你的鼻子，十分钟后再松开。” 爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天不要再捡核桃了。” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“连着弯几个小时腰可不行。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又一个捡核桃的受伤了。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊想回去继续捡核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，爸爸开着车回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊和爸爸说了几句话后，就向池塘走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸走向大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对乔伊来说，有一个坏消息。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天早上，核桃的价格又下降了，降到了10美分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，可怜的乔伊。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷摇了摇头。“她没时间了。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得她还能实现自己的目标吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。” 爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 现在，她至少需要再捡500磅。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在她需要更多的帮手了。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚从口袋里拿出了手机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我们需要打几个电话！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>